idle
Discworld player help
idle

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
idle - find out how long someone has been idle.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
idle <player>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Tells you how long a given person has been idle for.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> idle pinkfish
Ms Pinkfish has been idle for 2 minutes and 49 seconds.
.EI

